---
description: Apply the repository Laravel conventions when working in a Laravel codebase.
globs:
  - "**/*.php"
  - "config/**/*.php"
  - "routes/**/*.php"
  - "resources/views/**/*.blade.php"
  - "bootstrap/**/*.php"
  - "artisan"
  - "composer.json"
---

When this rule matches, read and follow `.github/instructions/laravel.instructions.md`.

Use that file as the canonical source for Laravel layering, validation, policies, queues, and Eloquent expectations.